          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Preventing Overdoses and Saving Lives Act 2.0</strong></p> <p>This bill reauthorizes through FY2027, modifies eligibility for, and otherwise makes changes to grants for increasing access to emergency treatments to reverse opioid overdoses (e.g., naloxone).</p>]]>
